<br>
I posted on here a few days ago, askign wether a 21 Druid should wear the Ulthork Tunic/BCP/Foremans.. many responses said BCP/Foremans based on what I was doing, since the 35 Hp drop on the Ulthork was sure to hurt me at my level...<br>
<br>
I now have a similar question, I am now Level 25 (Yes.. low.. but I'm Leveling Evey 2 Days Or So) and over the weekend i Bought myself a Paw Of Opolla, found a good price (2800) on it and couldnt say no. Up to this point I was using the combo of Springwood Club/CGS... But... I was flat broke after buying the Paw, so I traded my Crystalline Belt for 1000 and 2 Wolf Fur Slippers, and sold the Springwood for 2k. I bought the Crystalline Belt back for 1500, and am back up to 2k in the bank, with 2 pairs of Wolf Fur Slippers to sell... My question is this :<br>
<br>
At the moment I am using the combo Of Paw/CGS... Now, I dont even have a weapon at my disposal right now, I've been debating on going out and getting a Velium Etched Stone Mace/Wraithbone hammer for fairly cheap, but just to get me through the melee situations if I have too.. But, after grouping over the weekend without a weapon.. I'm not sure if I even need a Weapon, I havent had to engage in Melee the last few days, and I love the Wis of Paw/CGS.... thats question 1, spend money on a weapon, or no?<br>
<br>
secondly, (Voxfire, this is explaining my stuff, you have deleted my posts before just for saying my equipement, I am posting because I want peoples opinions, please leave this post be) here is my equipment, and I am stumped on where to improve next, I was thinking of picking up another trade skill, but those arent even all that profitable.. and with a few K in the bank there has to be some way to upgrade...<br>
<br>
Face-Platnium Ruby Viel<br>
Neck-Chrysoberyl Tailsman<br>
Head-Nightshade Wreath<br>
Earrings-2 Forest Loops<br>
Body-BCP<br>
Cloak-Kunzar (Yes.. maybe Molten)<br>
Arms-Ulthork<br>
Wrists-2 Runed Mithril Bracers<br>
Fingers-1 Velium Ring, 1 Platnium Jasper<br>
Legs-Gatorscale<br>
Boots-Wolf Fur Slippers<br>
Range-Dustscryers Ball<br>
Main Slot-Paw Of Opolla<br>
Secondary-Charred Guardian Shield<br>
Gloves-Gnome Skin<br>
Belt-Crystalline Belt<br>
<br>
I believe thats everything... I'm just wondering what the next step is for me, and hoping smoe of you elders could help out.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your time.<br>
<br>
Megolian Silverbane<br>
Level 25 (Non Twinked) Druid<br>
Waywatchers Of Kelethin <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugwynetwoodsister.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gwynet Woodsister</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(4/17/01 7:17:02 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Few More Questions...</span><hr size=1> You no longer need a weapon past 20 or so. Even to finish up a snared mob, it will be more efficient to sit down, med and cast a DoT.<br>
