<br>
You might want to keep a fast weapon to keep skills up (dunno why, I hardly ever melee anymore), but once they're maxed, hold the Paw and CGS. Shoot, I don't think I could pass a Paw up for 2800 either, nice deal :-) <p><b>Gallatin</b><p>
